title: GPT-5.2
description: The best model for coding and agentic tasks across industries
longDescription:
LakshX is built for high-velocity teams that need to cut through the noise. It is a multi-tenant Kanban platform that integrates company-wide intelligence via RAG-powered search, automated meeting transcriptions, and an intelligent engineering calendar. 

With features like Dual-View Kanban (Board & Table), Live Analytics, and smart automations, LakshX transforms project management from a chaotic chore into a streamlined, intuitive process.
mission: To provide a clutter-free, intelligent project management experience that empowers teams to focus on building, not managing.

title: GPT-5 mini
description: A faster, cost-efficient version of GPT-5 for well-defined tasks
longDescription:
Anvesh is an automated intelligence engine designed to identify opportunities where businesses lack digital footprints. By hunting for high-value businesses with zero online presence, it enables targeted outreach and growth strategies.

Built to empower freelancers and small agencies worldwide, Anvesh acts as a force multiplier, providing professional-grade tools to discover untapped markets without the high costs typically associated with enterprise intelligence platforms.
mission: To democratize access to market intelligence and empower small agencies to compete with industry giants.

title: GPT-5 nano
description: Fastest, most cost-efficient version of GPT-5
longDescription:
GPT-5 nano is built for ultra-low latency tasks that require immediate response times. It integrates edge-ready architecture with minimal resource updates, making it ideal for high-velocity applications.

With features like Edge Inference and Cost-Optimized Processing, GPT-5 nano transforms heavy AI workloads into streamlined, efficient operations.
mission: To provide a lightning-fast, cost-effective AI experience for high-volume applications.
